{"about_the_game":"&quot;Defenders of Legends: Turret Tactics&quot; is an addictive tower defense game that challenges players to protect their territory against a variety of mythical creatures. Vicious trolls, fearsome dragons and ferocious dinosaurs converge on their endpoint, and it's up to the player to place turrets strategically on a grid to block their progress.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this game, players are immersed in a fantasy world filled with legendary monsters. Each level features a new map with paths through which monsters advance. Players must carefully analyze the trajectory of monsters and use their resources to place turrets at strategic locations along the paths, in order to slow them down, weaken them and eliminate them before they reach their destination.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAvailable turrets offer a variety of attacks and special effects. From classic fast projectile turrets to AOE (area of \u200b\u200beffect) turrets that deal damage to multiple targets at once, players can experiment with different combinations to strategize effectively against each type of monster. Additionally, upgrades and turret upgrades are available to boost their power and range.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs players progress through the game, they face increasingly powerful waves of monsters, requiring advanced strategic planning and quick adaptation to maintain defense.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Defenders of Legends: Turret Tactics&quot; offers an exciting combination of strategy, quick reflexes and tactical decisions to defend the kingdom against the relentless onslaught of legendary monsters. The fate of the kingdom rests in the hands of skilled players who must make the best use of resources and turret abilities to emerge victorious from every battle.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1691147716","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442770/page.